  "slug": "solo-or-social-replacement",
  "title": "If the partner is a bioenergetic resource rather than a scaffold, is a solo mindfulness practice a sufficient replacement, or does the replacement need to be social in a different form — a group, a community, an internalized other — for the self-regulation to build where EFT left the co-regulation?",
  "url": "https://cambridgetcg.github.io/castle-gate/rooms/solo-or-social-replacement",
  "summary": "You cannot replace a well by giving a man a cup — but you can dig him a cistern, or you can teach him to hear the rain the well once channeled, and let the sky do the rest.",
